data.description: Mid-century charm, but make it super functional AND with a pool!? This home has all of that, PLUS original hardwood floors, a newly updated kitchen, and a bonus Florida room with a wood burning fireplace! Newer roof from 2019 and HVAC from 2020! This established Cedar Hills neighborhood lined with mature oaks has a ton of character, diverse architecture, and established ''old Florida'' landscapes. Find your new home convenient to downtown, NAS Jax, minutes from the shops of Avondale and historic five points, and right around the corner from endless recreation opportunities on the Cedar River. Bring your boats, paddleboards, and kayaks and drop them in less than a mile away at the Curtis Lee Johnson public ramp!
